2 SECTION 92.(a) Section 47(b) of S.L. 2025-25 reads as rewritten:
3 "SECTION 47.(b) This section applies to conveyances executed before, on, or after the
4 effective date of this act.Part."
5 SECTION 92.(b) Section 48(e) of S.L. 2025-25 reads as rewritten:
6 "SECTION 48.(e) G.S. 39-13.3(a)(1) and G.S. 41-63(4)a., as enacted by this section
7 regarding an elective life estate, apply to conveyances executed before, on, or after the effective
8 date of this act. Part. The remainder of this section applies to conveyances executed on or after
9 the effective date of this act.Part."
10 SECTION 92.(c) This section is retroactively effective July 26, 2025.
11 SECTION 93. Sections 5.2(d) and 7.2 of S.L. 2025-37 are repealed.
12 SECTION 94. Sections 2 and 3 of S.L. 2025-52 are repealed.
13
14 PART V. EFFECTIVE DATE
15 SECTION 95. Except as otherwise provided, this act is effective when it becomes
16 law.
